name: Silvon
note: <cgmzdesc:That's me. I'm kind of just your basic run-of-the-mill knight, but with some cool magic powers to boot! I'm admittedly a bit of a shut-in most of the time, but I try my best when I get out there!>
profile: A nerdy swordsman with psychic powers. Doesn't get out much, but just enough to be a hero.

name: Fizzler
note: <cgmzdesc:That's Fizzler. She's very energetic and sweet. She's like a sister to me! She's an expert in fire magic, having the ability to cast magic with wands and even with just her bare hands! She usually wears a mask all about, but here she's much happier with her appearance which is nice to see...>
profile:
A very hyperactive girl that is the fire element 
personified.

name: Hollvor
note: <cgmzdesc:That's Hollvor. Similarly he is like a brother to me... poor guy got in an incident a while back and lost the ability to speak, but he is able to use magic for that now. He excels at speaking telepathically! He's also very strong and tanky... and athletic too. I look up to him sometimes...>
profile:
A silent and powerful force to be reckoned with. 
Very tanky.

name: Judy
note: <cgmzdesc:That's Judy. She's a very intelligent lady that we met somewhat recently in Ciucereza City... back in the real Santotierra. She's very agile and cool! I never thought she'd be so good at combat, but I guess the leveling up here helps out a ton. Still a bit fragile though...>
profile:
An intellectual and swift yet somewhat frail rabbit 
lady who likes to help as much as she can.

name: Willy
note: <cgmzdesc:I have no idea who the hell this is, but anyone for our team is good enough for me! He kinda makes me uncomfortable though. Who the hell doesn't aim?! And where is he from... certainly not from Santotierra.>
profile:
Or John. Whatever you prefer. Somewhere in his mid 
30s, very confusing, but the swaggiest goat ever.
